{% extends 'VegaLiteAgent/improvement_step.jinja2' %}

{% block instructions %}
Add helpful tooltips and axis titles for better user experience.

# SCOPE: Interactivity & Axis Labels
Focus on:
- encoding.tooltip (array of fields with titles and formatting)
- encoding.x.title (axis label, not chart title)
- encoding.y.title (axis label, not chart title)
- mark.point or mark.tooltip (only if needed for tooltip interactivity)

DO NOT modify:
- Top-level title object (chart title/subtitle)
- encoding.color
- mark.type (keep the chart type the same)
{% endblock %}

{% block examples %}
Bar chart with tooltips:
```yaml
encoding:
  tooltip:
  - field: state
    title: State
    type: ordinal
  - field: avg_pcap
    format: .2f
    title: Avg Power Capacity
    type: quantitative
  x:
    field: avg_pcap
    type: quantitative
    title: "Average Power Capacity (MW)"
  y:
    field: state
    type: ordinal
    title: "State"
```

Line chart with tooltips (needs point overlay):
```yaml
mark:
  type: line
  point: true
  tooltip: true
encoding:
  tooltip:
  - field: year
    title: Year
    type: quantitative
  - field: value
    format: .2f
    title: Value
    type: quantitative
  x:
    field: year
    type: quantitative
    title: "Year"
  y:
    field: value
    type: quantitative
    title: "Value"
```
{% endblock %}

